clipboard-extension (1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial packaging of the Clipboard GNOME Shell extension.
  * Installs to /usr/share/gnome-shell/extensions/clipboard@haibachvan.local/
    and the GSettings schema to /usr/share/glib-2.0/schemas/.
  * Targets GNOME Shell 49/50 on Wayland.

